## Start pipewire as a PulseAudio replacement
exec pipewire
exec pipewire-pulse

## Keybindings
bindsym XF86AudioLowerVolume exec pactl set-sink-volume $audio_sink -2%
bindsym XF86AudioRaiseVolume exec pactl set-sink-volume $audio_sink +2%
bindsym XF86AudioMute exec pactl set-sink-mute $audio_sink toggle
